{
  "description": "简化版Google搜索工具集成示例",
  "request": {
    "url": "https://x666.me/v1/chat/completions",
    "method": "POST",
    "headers": {
      "authorization": "Bearer your-api-key",
      "Content-Type": "application/json"
    },
    "body": {
      "messages": [
        {
          "role": "user",
          "content": "关于openai和超级碗相关的新闻有什么"
        }
      ],
      "model": "gemini-2.5-flash-preview-05-20",
      "stream": false,
      "tools": [
        {
          "type": "function",
          "function": {
            "name": "googleSearch"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "notes": [
    "工具定义已简化，只包含必要的name字段",
    "避免了复杂的参数定义导致的API兼容性问题",
    "只有Gemini模型且启用联网搜索时才会添加此工具",
    "系统会自动检测模型类型并决定是否添加工具"
  ]
}